---
// src/pages/index.astro
// Hauptseite für den Cloud Identity Summit 2026
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Cloud Identity Summit 2026 | Frankfurt am Main</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Die führende Community-Konferenz für Cloud Identity, Security und Governance im deutschsprachigen Raum." />
    
    <!-- Hier weisen wir Astro an, die installierte Tailwind-Konfiguration nativ einzubinden -->
    <style is:global>
        @tailwind base;
        @tailwind components;
        @tailwind utilities;
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 min-h-screen font-sans antialiased selection:bg-blue-500/30">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="border-b border-slate-900 bg-slate-950/70 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold tracking-tight text-lg">
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-400">Cloud Identity</span> Summit
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400">
                <a href="#about" class="hover:text-white transition">Über das Event</a>
                <a href="#team" class="hover:text-white transition">Team</a>
                <a href="https://cloudinspires.me" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition">Podcast</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="#tickets" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10">
                    Tickets folgen
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-24 px-6 border-b border-slate-900">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-400 font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-blue-950/40 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-blue-900/40">
                ⚡ Community Konferenz · Zero Trust & Identity
            </span>
            
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-6 mb-8 leading-[1.1]">
                Identity. Security.<br />
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-cyan-400 to-indigo-500">Enterprise Governance.</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
                Nach dem Erfolg der letzten Jahre bringen wir die führenden Köpfe, Microsoft MVPs und Identity-Enthusiasten wieder zusammen. Ein Tag voller Deep-Dives, Networking und praxisnaher Security.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm font-mono text-slate-300">
                <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800/80 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl backdrop-blur flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span>📅</span> <strong>3. November 2026</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800/80 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl backdrop-blur flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span>📍</span> <strong>Frankfurt am Main</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Info Section -->
    <section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="text-blue-500 text-2xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Pure Focus</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Kein Marketing-Sprech. Nur knallharte technische Sessions zu Microsoft Entra, Purview, Zero Trust und dezentralen Identitäten.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="text-cyan-400 text-2xl mb-4">👥</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">By the Community</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Organisiert von Community-Leads und MVPs für IT-Architekten, Security-Verantwortliche und Cloud-Consultants.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="text-indigo-400 text-2xl mb-4">🌐</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Networking</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Triff Gleichgesinnte im Herzen von Frankfurt, tausche dich in den Pausen aus und erweitere dein Experten-Netzwerk.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="border-t border-slate-900 bg-slate-950 py-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-slate-400">
            <div>&copy; 2026 Cloud Identity Summit. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</div>
            <div class="flex gap-6 text-slate-500 text-xs">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Impressum</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition">Datenschutz</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>